title: CFL 1981 Tiger-Cats vs. Roughriders
description:
Canadian Football League game featuring the Hamilton Tiger-Cats visiting the Saskatchewan Roughriders at Taylor Field, Regina, in 1981.

A few glitches (originally recorded with first generation VHS technology). Still not bad, given the tapes are 27 years old!

While not one of the better Roughrider games of that season, the 4th quarter had some very memorable moments, including two touchdowns in an 8 second interval.

DVD (NTSC 4:3) format.
